data.text:
CAREER HONORS

OSU Scholar Athlete (2023)

AS A FRESHMAN (2023)

Competed with the gray trio and team her first season as a Buckeye

Made her Ohio State debut in team at the Jessica Beck Memorial Competition in the team routine

Swam at the 2023 U.S. Collegiate National Championship meet, helping the team to the overall institution title

PRIOR TO OHIO STATE

Member of the Granite Club synchronized swimming team

2022 Junior Canadian National Technical Solo Champion

Finalist in team and duet at the Youth Worlds in 2019

2019 Canadian National Solo and Figure Champion

PERSONAL

Daughter of Tina and Simon Gray

Has one sibling: Jack

Majoring in biology

Plans to attend medical school or become a scientist following graduation
